data.description: Come and enjoy this truly move in ready, beautifully maintained home on one of the largest lots in the Ridge. Enjoy the private, stunning fully fenced backyard, deck and paver patios perfect for entertaining and morning coffee. Generous 3 car tandem garage opening to side yard provides storage for kayaks, SUP's and more. Gourmet kitchen with Sub Zero and Viking appliances. Lovely cabinetry, built ins and walk in pantry. Both Primary suite and additional on suite sport new showers and more upgrades. The secret bonus off the master is the perfect retreat, office or work out room. Upgraded lighting and exquisite built ins throughout. Freshly painted inside and out, upgraded garage doors, Sonos, front door, custom metal fencing, mature landscape, gorgeous trees and flowers. Complete list of upgrades, features and artistic details attached.
